msgid "Defeat a God!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../JOU_god.rst:7
# 2994dc7066774a4392abff373fcd4a60
msgid "Xenagps has thrown all of Theros into disarray with his ascension to godhood. His euphoric revels threaten to plunge the plane into chaos. There is only one way to silence this revel once and for all: isolate Xenagos and vanquish him."
msgstr ""

#: ../../JOU_god.rst:11
# 647c0fbed313426fba9ba1b8189def71
msgid "The party starts small, with only Xenagos and a few of his revelers, but that relative calm will not last for long. More and more revelers will join as the battle continues. They are violently erratic, attacking without warning one moment and pausing to celebrate the next. Xenagos will even attack you directly when the mood strikes him. As long as the revel continues and revelers surround him, he is untouchable. But a god who loses all his followers is vulnerable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../JOU_god.rst:18
# 34658654bf8646f89e4f10b978c2d147
msgid "Is your destiny a heroic victory or death at the hands of the divine? Xenagos awaits."
msgstr ""

